# BhanksDAO Governance Guide

## Overview
BhanksDAO is on-chain governance where BHNK
holders vote on protocol decisions.
Voting power equals your BHNK balance.

## How to create a proposal
1. Connect your wallet on the DAO page
2. Make sure you hold BHNK tokens
3. Click Create Proposal
4. Write a clear description
5. Confirm the transaction
6. Voting opens immediately for 7 days

## How to vote
1. Go to the DAO page
2. Find an active proposal
3. Click Vote For or Vote Against
4. Confirm in your wallet
5. Your vote is recorded on-chain permanently

## How proposals pass
- Voting period of 7 days has ended
- Votes For is greater than Votes Against
- Anyone can then call execute() to finalize

## Ideas for proposals
- Change the staking reward rate
- Set a new NFT mint price
- Approve a community airdrop
- Add a new protocol feature